      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride or a fun project car? This vehicle is priced to move and offers a fantastic opportunity for the handy buyer or DIY enthusiast! It does show its age with some wear and mechanical needs, so it's best suited for someone ready to put in a little TLC. At this price point, you're getting a solid starting point without breaking the bank \u2014 come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
